      "term": "servente",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "A2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "A person employed to do basic or domestic work, or to assist in tasks that do not require specialized training.",
          "examples": [
            "The servent-turned-helper cleaned the kitchen after the meal.",
            "In some offices, a servent helps with filing and tidying the workspace."
